On this occasion, your deal was not successful for selection. We make our selections based on a range of criteria including, but not limited to, the following:

• Market-leading value: Our customers should not be able to find the exact same product at a better price by visiting other retailers for the duration of the deal period.
• Relevancy for customers:– products on offer should be from category areas that are seasonally relevant or in demand.
• Sufficient stock: The product should be nominated as a deal in sufficient quantities to be available for the majority of the duration of the deal period.
• Breadth of selection: It's important that we provide eBay customers with a breadth of selection and, as a result, we may select a range of offers that represents the full range of choice at eBay.

We hope you next nomination is successful and that you submit another deal again soon.

